juniOspfAgent.name: juniOspfAgent

revisions.description: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names.
New objects were added to the Juniper-OSPF-MIB juniOspfBasicGroup2.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniOspfAgent.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@Juniper.net
juniOspfAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Open Shortest Path First (OSPF) routing protocol component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniOspfAgentV1.name: juniOspfAgentV1
juniOspfAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the OSPF component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the OSPF component was supported in JUNOSe 2.x and 3.x system
        releases.
juniOspfAgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the OSPF application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when new objects were added to the juniOspfBasicGroup.

juniOspfAgentV2.name: juniOspfAgentV2
juniOspfAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the OSPF component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the OSPF component is supported in JUNOSe 4.0 and subsequent system
        releases.
juniOspfAgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the OSPF application in JUNOSe.
